Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:05.48,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:06.02,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:11.74,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell am I doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:14.07,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:17.95,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,How did you end up eating breakfast at our place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:20.70,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,And you! Why aren't you bothered by it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:27.58,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I be? Since she is so small she doesn't take up much space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:31.51,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's more delicious when you eat breakfast with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:34.17,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Give me another helping already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:44.94,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I cooked enough for three. How much do you intend to eat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:51.11,Default,Inko,0000,0000,0000,,T-Timoten.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.39,0:00:56.03,Ep Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(523,275)}Ryuuji and Taiga
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:57.57,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, are you trying to make your pet molt from stress?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:00:59.94,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it get any uglier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.94,0:01:01.11,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call it ugly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.32,0:01:04.32,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,In truth, pets are similar to their owners.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.32,0:01:05.57,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.57,0:01:07.24,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You ungrateful little—!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.24,0:01:10.41,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Have some respect for me! I made you breakfast {\i1}and{\i0}  prepared a lunchbox!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.41,0:01:12.42,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you mongrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:14.79,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Mon—! Calling me that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.79,0:01:17.84,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Give the lunchbox back! Give my kindness back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:19.96,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and rot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.63,0:01:22.63,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up, Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.09,0:01:27.35,Narration,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that late-night attack, Aisaka Taiga has begun appearing at our dinner table.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:25.43,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(357,358)\3c&HFFFCF7&\fnVAG Rounded Std Light\b0\c&H615245&\frz1.429}School Road
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.47,0:01:28.81,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:29.39,Alt,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:31.10,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:34.73,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,once we get to school, make sure that you properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:38.57,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,between Kitamura-kun and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:41.44,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,um... mediate things between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:45.82,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You promised me you'd work like a dog for me, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:48.12,Narration,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,...things have ended up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:50.91,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If things seem to take a bad turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:52.34,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:54.71,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:57.21,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Good to see you perky today, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.21,0:01:59.34,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:01.71,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? You're kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:04.38,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, I had no idea that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:09.01,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga and Takasu-kun are now in a\Ncompanioned, commuting relationship!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.01,0:02:09.89,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it all wr—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.89,0:02:12.43,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You know, people don't use\N"companioned" like that these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:13.31,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:16.56,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right. These days, they say...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:20.52,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Egads, I don't know what they call it these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:22.19,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, how about "togethered"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:23.28,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:26.91,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to stumble upon Aisaka over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:27.70,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Ais—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:30.12,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so it was just a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:31.37,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently we live close to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.37,0:02:32.55,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.37,0:02:32.87,Alt,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:35.50,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you later, Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:37.58,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, I was watching TV and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:45.72,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I get it now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:50.69,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to get closer to Kushieda, I'll first have to mediate between Aisaka and Kitamura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:53.06,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Let's bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:58.90,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,And that's it for shooting practice. Onwards, we'll pair u-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:00.53,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Aisaka. Let's pair up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:03.11,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's pair up, Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.24,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:06.19,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,...up and pass balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:09.04,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, Aisaka, you two are really fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:10.28,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:12.49,Alt,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that kind of a day today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:12.49,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The plan is simple.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:15.75,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll lightly peg Kitamura's partner with the ball.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:16.96,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:20.92,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you'll cause a big fuss and take his partner to the infirmary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:25.17,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thus, Aisaka and Kitamura will lose their partners, and pair up instead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:28.13,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,Maruo! Let's pair up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:33.26,Alt,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,Who'll be wanting to team up with Haruto-kun today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.13,0:03:31.76,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing. And stop calling me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:33.26,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,But you're so similar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.05,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:37.98,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kitamura-kun's pairing up with that weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.31,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:40.60,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Events have taken a turn for the weir—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:41.27,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.86,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,Want to pair up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:44.69,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.69,0:03:46.15,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Even Kushieda...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:48.49,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,The plan will continue regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:49.53,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—? But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:52.57,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what gender his partner is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:57.08,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,And the swelling bulges drawn in the Jouan era...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:03:58.66,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Haruta?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:01.88,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll throw the ball without using my thumbs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:06.30,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,That didn't reach me, Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:10.38,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,The road to understanding the Satoru-ball is steep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:10.80,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:13.97,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind me, not everyone knows about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:16.01,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That Noto...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:17.02,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:20.65,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey! Hey! Pass, pass! Pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.77,0:04:22.27,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go, Maruo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:23.06,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:25.73,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Nice form.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:27.98,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying, Maruo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:30.61,Alt,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,No, really, that was very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.36,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:30.99,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Pass, you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:32.28,Alt,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:34.16,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,But pegging a girl with the ball...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:34.20,Alt,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:35.21,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pass!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:39.12,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Kihara. I will atone for this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:42.67,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Clone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:45.04,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Maruo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:48.59,Default,Chatter,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:50.38,Default,Chatter,0000,0000,0000,,The Palmtop Tiger got taken down by Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:52.01,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}O-Oops.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:55.76,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTora Ep Titles\3c&HDCE3E2&\fs25\c&H505358&\pos(365,151)}Home Economics Practice Room
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:55.76,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Palmtop Tiger snarls at whoever's around.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:05:01.81,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even so, she's trying so hard that she makes a fool of herself,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:05.27,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so you just end up wanting to help her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:12.91,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, you {\i1}have{\i0}  to hand them over casually
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.28,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:17.66,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:19.20,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,As nonchalantly as possible, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:23.79,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Thoughtlessly, informally, frivolously...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:24.42,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:28.75,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, where's Kitamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:33.51,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for Kitamura, he said he had some business over at building B or some—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:34.22,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:36.18,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,He just left, so he might be that wa-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:37.68,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:38.51,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Follow him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.51,0:05:39.51,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:40.93,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:42.60,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:51.90,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,She's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:55.03,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At that speed, she'll catch him—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:07.88,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Are the cookies okay...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:11.63,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:16.93,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought. It's swollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:24.64,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find the cookies?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:27.31,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Were they okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:30.90,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:39.99,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:43.83,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I might just be a klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:46.04,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She wasn't aware of that already?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:50.34,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If I write a love letter, I end up putting it in the wrong bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:53.42,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If I try to invade a house, I fall over from hunger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:56.97,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If I play basketball, I get a ball right in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:07:00.80,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If I try to hand over some cookies, I fall down the stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:02.51,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Dropping the cookies...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:05.77,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, there's more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:08.06,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Like forgetting to put the love letter inside the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:09.65,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,There was that, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:26.00,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Give me one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:31.04,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wait, they {\i1}are{\i0}  smashed into pieces...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:32.17,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And besides they t—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:39.97,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,They're great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:42.89,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,They came out okay, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:46.43,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame. Let's try harder next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:59.07,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I {\i1}did{\i0}  see them. They were buying things like spring onions and radishes at the supermarket. Are they like, married?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:59.07,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fnTora Ep Titles\fs22\3a&H96&\pos(73,380)}Statement, Witness #1, Year 2 Class C, H-To K-ji
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:05.04,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}They left the same apartment building together with naughty looks on their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:05.04,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fnTora Ep Titles\fs22\3a&H96&\pos(73,380)}Statement, Witness #2, Year 2 Class C, K-hara M-ya
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:10.00,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Also, they were feeding each other homemade cookies saying, "Here, open up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:10.00,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fnTora Ep Titles\fs22\3a&H96&\pos(73,380)}Statement, Witness #3, Year 2 Class C, N-to H-mitsu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:13.50,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fnTora Ep Titles\fs22\3a&H96&\pos(73,380)}Statement, Witness #4, Year 2 Class C, K-shii N-nako
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:13.50,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0010,,{\an8}Really? Are they like that? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:18.01,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Minorin. What's up with your best friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.18,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:27.64,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get inside already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:29.35,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,My.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:30.48,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,"My"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.23,0:08:33.56,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,May I have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:40.86,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,The sun is dry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:43.70,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with Kushieda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:44.70,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:45.49,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:47.08,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! What, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:58.67,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Please take good care of Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:00.13,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:02.84,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga is my dearest best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:06.64,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Please bestow happiness upon her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:09.27,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kushieda. Are you saying you're—?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:10.43,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.81,0:09:15.36,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:17.90,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,You must be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:20.11,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura? What're you doing up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:22.70,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering why you were together so often,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:25.41,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,but now that I think about it, you two fit together so well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:28.41,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka! Get yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:30.50,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You! Stop laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:31.75,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:35.88,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,If you make Taiga cry... I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:47.93,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kushi... eda...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:50.89,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:56.65,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin misunderstood everything because I was intruding at your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:58.23,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:09:59.32,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Your place was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:02.61,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,really cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:10.08,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I struggled so much with my parents that when I said I wanted to leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.83,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,they simply gave me that apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:14.50,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I knew they were those kind of parents, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.63,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,The cookies were salty, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:21.80,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I was frustrated when I found them in pieces, so I ate some.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:24.17,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,They were horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.18,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you ate all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:27.80,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You even lied about their taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:31.35,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Even as a mongrel, your fur will shed if you keep being so nice to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:33.02,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:38.73,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you also get troubled while thinking about Minori?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:40.44,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:42.69,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess you would...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.11,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.11,0:10:50.58,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't anyone understand us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.49,0:10:57.37,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're so troubled, why doesn't anyone support us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:59.84,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,In truth, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:02.84,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's... Everyone's... Everyone's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:07.51,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Piss{\alpha&HFF&}ing me off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:07.88,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pissing {\alpha&HFF&}me off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:08.18,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pissing me {\alpha&HFF&}off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:10.05,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pissing me off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:11.76,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Pissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:12.51,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Pissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:13.52,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Pissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:14.80,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the Palmtop Tiger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.52,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not okay with being that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:18.90,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.02,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:22.77,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you listen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:25.61,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Even mom, even dad, no one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:29.91,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Understands me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:35.20,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:40.42,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a problem with me being small?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:41.42,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me a delinquent just because of my appearance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:43.13,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a problem with us being together in front of everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:44.96,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for having evil-looking eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.26,0:11:51.14,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.76,0:11:54.22,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuji, isn't this pole tilted now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:55.60,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's not poss—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:57.46,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}is{\i0}  tilted!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:58.27,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:01.15,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:03.27,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,We won, we won!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.36,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:08.95,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, I will confess to Kitamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:11.70,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It'll all be over then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:12.82,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Over?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:15.16,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Your services as a dog will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:19.41,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,As of tomorrow, we're just classmates who live close to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.12,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And that's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:27.26,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye, Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:32.59,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:39.02,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:41.57,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we having breakfast really early today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:44.69,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yacchan likes canned mackerel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:49.36,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Is Taiga-chan still sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:50.57,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:54.24,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:55.41,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, we didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:03.54,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:04.34,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:06.46,Default,Inko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.89,0:13:22.10,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:33.61,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Did she...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:39.79,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takasu, we're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:41.66,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,We spread all those weird rumors...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:43.38,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka-san got mad at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:44.42,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:46.83,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,"There's nothing between me and Ryuuji."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:50.00,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Saying you're not a delinquent, making a huge mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:53.38,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,She really is scary, the Palmtop Tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:57.05,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,But I said that Takasu isn't as scary as he looks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:58.64,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,What, when did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:01.39,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, shouldn't we clean this up real fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:02.27,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.68,0:14:04.82,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:06.60,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,A-About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:09.07,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You see, Taiga was saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:13.03,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm absolutely not going out with Takasu-kun."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:15.66,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,"So this is all a misunderstanding."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:17.99,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,She especially wanted me to be aware of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:24.30,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,And she had this kind of desperate, serious look about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:26.30,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,But does that mean she...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:28.25,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean she—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:29.79,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know, Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:33.05,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:34.88,Alt,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What does she think she's doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:37.10,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Weren't you going to confess to Kitamura today?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:39.85,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't the time to be worrying about me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:44.48,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,As of tomorrow, we're just classmates who live close to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:46.94,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And that's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:57.45,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"And that's all there is to it"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:00.28,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.74,0:15:01.45,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:04.16,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I... Kitamura-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:07.12,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun... I....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:11.38,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Um, uh... I, uh... That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:15.42,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why are you doing it right after arriving at school?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:19.01,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If things don't turn out well, this will be one hell of a bad day, you know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:20.05,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Um, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:21.27,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:26.14,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,I think I get how this conversation will spell out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:29.61,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, I would like to verify something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:32.77,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you dating Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:35.36,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's just Minorin misunderstanding things!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:37.36,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:39.78,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:41.62,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:44.25,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Our houses just happen to be close to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:47.58,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with liking him or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:49.17,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Then, do you dislike him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:56.64,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't dislike him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.93,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:05.35,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you see, Takasu-kun is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:07.06,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, fried rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:11.27,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji made me delicious fried rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:13.32,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,He cheered me up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:16.73,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,He even lied to make me feel better...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:19.12,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Being there for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:23.70,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Because Ryuuji was there, because he was supporting me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:29.67,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, I'm now capable of standing here like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:33.96,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love with you, Kitamura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:39.63,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aisaka, you're amazing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:41.56,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:47.19,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I think your feelings were properly relayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:49.64,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:54.23,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Do you recall one year ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:55.44,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:58.11,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike that time, you now have this
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:00.61,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,funny-looking face!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:03.20,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Funny face?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:08.21,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, when you're around Takasu, you have this funny-looking face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:10.66,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu's a great guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:15.63,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,And you, thinking of him like you did earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:18.18,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,makes you a wonderful girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:22.47,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Like I did earlier...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:24.64,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:28.93,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm relieved you're on such good terms with Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:30.64,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:32.56,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji doesn't have anything to do-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:34.10,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,My face was looking funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:38.23,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,My feet, what about my feet? Wait, what am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:39.65,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Was I able to tell you I love you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:41.03,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be okay, Aisaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.61,0:17:42.36,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:44.24,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to be okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:46.12,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't understood what I was saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:51.21,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay, from now on, I'm sure we'll be great friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:53.87,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'm saying, not friends, I was confess—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:56.17,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Friends...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.42,0:17:58.50,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:05.76,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, we'll be late for homeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:07.47,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Better hurry up, Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:19.69,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were going to start crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:24.36,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You! D-Did you see all of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:25.49,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I did, but I didn't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:26.75,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,"Didn't mean to"? You—!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:28.28,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,But what're you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:31.71,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.21,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:37.46,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:39.46,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't had breakfast, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:41.43,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,And did you even eat last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:43.42,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you went to the convenie—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:44.51,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:48.85,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Why? If you do that again, people will start misunderstanding again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:51.43,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you you don't have to do this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:56.23,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:59.19,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't leave you alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:01.44,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you it's enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:03.94,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You're no longer my dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:05.83,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:09.32,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am not a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:11.45,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:15.87,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, I'm able to be by your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:16.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Ais-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.58,0:19:19.42,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:22.46,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,"Taiga"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:26.01,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Since the ancient times, the dragon has been the only beast that could equally stand with a tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:28.01,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:32.85,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,And thus, as a dragon, I'll be able to be at your side, tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.06,0:19:42.98,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,There's a limit to how impudent you can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:42.94,Alt,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.98,0:19:44.61,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Know your place already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.61,0:19:45.69,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:47.99,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:49.74,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, I'm hungry, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:50.61,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.07,0:19:53.20,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And we're going to make a new plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:56.41,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not giving up on Kitamura-kun just from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:19:58.71,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:01.33,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter whether you're a dog or a dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:06.42,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Since you said you'd be at my side, you better work hard, Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:10.05,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Did I decide on this too quickly...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:12.14,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Come on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:13.68,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:21.77,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He said, "Taiga."{\i0}
