Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:28.08,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0005,,Heart-warming girl, Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:29.58,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0005,,Ah, you're Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:32.45,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0005,,Always shining so brightly with joy!
